    <mxCell id="55" value="Two-scale SSL pre-training:
· Within-panel masking (40% per panel)
  → learns test co-deviation patterns
· Cross-panel dropout (whole panel)
  → learns inter-system dependencies" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fffde7;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;strokeColor=#f9a825;fontSize=9;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="630" y="545" width="520" height="82" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="56" value="Parallel Design Philosophy
Both encoders extract features at
multiple depth levels (shallow→deep)
and concatenate for richer representations." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="480" y="560" width="120" height="100" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
